<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>PHP sample app</title>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <style>
        body{
            position: relative;
        }
        h1 {

            font-family: 'Lato';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 30px;
            line-height: 36px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #414D97;
        }
        p {
            font-family: 'Lato';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #414D97;
        }
        a {
            color: #4CA8E0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .userInformation {
            position: absolute;
            display: block;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 13px;
            width: 20%;
            line-height: 13px;
            right: 0;
        }

        .userInformation div {
            color: #9452BA;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            padding-right: 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .header {
            position: sticky;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9452BA;
            height: 60px;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            left: 100px;
            top: 100px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <div>UserInformation</div>
</div>

<div class="content">

    <h1>Congratulations!</h1>

    <p>You’ve got your App token and<b>&nbspyou’re ready to query the PIM API.</b></p>

    <p>
    To do so, open the following page <a href="/first-api-call" target="_blank">&nbsp’first-API-call’</a>.
    If you want to have a look at the HTTP client, open the file <b><i>&nbsp’src/UseCase/FirstApiCall.php’</i></b>.</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
